445
00:58:59.380 --> 00:59:01.850
Have some water. You must be tired.

446
00:59:02.180 --> 00:59:03.780
Did you drive from Bangkok?

447
00:59:04.990 --> 00:59:06.010
Yes.

448
00:59:09.120 --> 00:59:13.150
